description: Learn the secret to making the best Greek meatballs, also known as keftedes, with Roula from Greece. Her traditional meatball recipe is flavoured with cumin, oregano, mint and parsley then shallow-fried — it’s been perfected in her kitchen over the last 25 years. A favourite among her family, this recipe is sure to be a hit among the fussiest of eaters. Serve with Greek salad, rice or pasta.
name: AUTHENTIC Greek Meatballs
